##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                1028 1451
                                                                  1028 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       1028 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  1028 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   1028 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  1028 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  1028 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 1028 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   1028 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:1028 1451
